(124,3,'2015-02-15 15:36:39','2015-02-15 12:36:39','<h6>DMD, General Dentist, Canada\r\nUmm Suqeim Clinic</h6>\r\n<div class=\"justext\">\r\n\r\nDr. Soulaf Shaker is a general dentist whose passion centers on cosmetic dentistry and endodontics. Her practice philosophy is to give her patients a perfect smile and a comfortable and stress-free experience using the latest advances in dentistry.\r\n\r\nIn 2010, Dr. Soulaf graduated from the University of British Columbia - Faculty of Dentistry in Canada and got certified to perform numerous treatments under moderate and nitrous oxide sedation for patients with mild to severe dental anxiety. She previously earned her degree from Baghdad University - Faculty of Dentistry, Iraq in 1997 and has since grew her practice serving in both public and private sectors. She was an active participant in government programs that provide subsidized dentistry to people living in rural areas.\r\n\r\n“When it comes to patients smile and dental health, I strive to have the most advanced training and technology to provide patients with the best dental experience. It’s that kind of experience that gives my patients the confidence to refer their families and friends back.”\r\n\r\nShe is a member of the Royal College of Dental Surgeons of Ontario and the Canadian Dental Association. She speaks fluent English, Arabic, Kurdish and basic Turkish.\r\n\r\nDr. Soulaf is happily married and has two children. Outside of dentistry, she enjoys traveling and cooking Middle Eastern dishes and pastries. She is a firm believer in giving back to the community and is very passionate in supporting charities and children in need.\r\n\r\n</div>','Dr. Soulaf Shaker','','publish','closed','closed','','dr-soulaf-shaker','','','2015-02-15 15:36:48','2015-02-15 12:36:48','',0,'http://demo2.saitobaza.ru/?post_type=dentalist&#038;p=124',0,'dentalist','',0),
